AndStatus is a light-weight Twitter and pump.io client for Android 
([http://identi.ca/ identi.ca] is now one of the sites of the [http://pump.io/ pump.io social network]). 
It supports multiple User accounts and allows you to read messages (tweets, timelines and conversations), 
send Status updates and Direct messages, create Favorites etc. even when you are offline or in bad connection conditions. Open Source License.

[http://andstatus.org AndStatus project] was created in December 2011 as a  
community initiative, not associated with any person, commercial entity and not tied to Twitter only.
Since that time the project made substantial progress, 
see the [https://github.com/andstatus/andstatus/wiki/changelog Change Log].

For more information please read the [https://github.com/andstatus/andstatus/wiki AndStatus Wiki]. 
